trans-unit.source: Defines an <xref:System.Windows.Input.ICommand> that is routed through the element tree and contains a text property.
trans-unit.target: Meghatározza egy <xref:System.Windows.Input.ICommand>, hogy az elem fájában keresztül történik, és szöveges tulajdonságot tartalmaz.</xref:System.Windows.Input.ICommand>

trans-unit.source: The difference between a RoutedUICommand and <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand> is that RoutedUICommand includes a <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedUICommand.Text%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: A különbség a között egy RoutedUICommand és <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand>hogy RoutedUICommand része egy <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedUICommand.Text%2A>tulajdonság.</xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedUICommand.Text%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand.Execute%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand.CanExecute%2A> methods on a <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand> do not contain the command logic for the command, as is the case with a typical <xref:System.Windows.Input.ICommand>.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand.Execute%2A>és <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand.CanExecute%2A>a <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand>nem tartalmazzák a parancs logikát a parancs, mint a szokásos <xref:System.Windows.Input.ICommand>.</xref:System.Windows.Input.ICommand> esetében</xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand> metódusai</xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand.CanExecute%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand.Execute%2A>

trans-unit.source: These methods raise events that traverse the element tree looking for an object with a <xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandBinding>.
trans-unit.target: Ezek a módszerek indíthat eseményeket, amelyek a fastruktúrán elem <xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandBinding>.</xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandBinding> objektum keresése

trans-unit.source: The event handlers attached to the <xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandBinding> contain the command logic.
trans-unit.target: Az eseménykezelők csatolva a <xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandBinding>tartalmazzák a parancs logikát.</xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandBinding>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand.Execute%2A> method raises the <xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandManager.PreviewExecuted> and <xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandManager.Executed> events.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand.Execute%2A>metódus vet fel a <xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandManager.PreviewExecuted>és <xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandManager.Executed>események.</xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandManager.Executed> </xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandManager.PreviewExecuted> </xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand.Execute%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand.CanExecute%2A> method raises the <xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandManager.PreviewCanExecute> and <xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandManager.CanExecute> events.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand.CanExecute%2A>metódus vet fel a <xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandManager.PreviewCanExecute>és <xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandManager.CanExecute>események.</xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandManager.CanExecute> </xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandManager.PreviewCanExecute> </xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand.CanExecute%2A>
